  <div class="w3-container w3-padding-large" style="margin-bottom:32px">
    <h2>A Timeless Tale of Tradition</h2>
      <p>Odisha's paper mache masks, or 'Mukha', are more than just vibrant faces. They're a narrative woven from eco-friendly materials, steeped in cultural heritage, and pulsating with the artistic brilliance of Odia artisans.</p>
      <p>These masks hold a mirror to Odisha's soul, reflecting stories from folklore, epics, and everyday life. From depicting deities to portraying theatrical characters, each mask is a unique masterpiece.</p>
      <div class="container">
        <h2>About Raghurajpur Paper Mache Masks</h2>
        <p>Raghurajpur, a heritage village in Odisha, is renowned for its exquisite handcrafted paper mache masks. Learn about the rich cultural heritage and craftsmanship behind these masks.</p>
    </div>
